<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFTushnet.2C_Mark_V..3B_Martin.2C_Francisco_Forrest.3B_Stephen_J._Schnably.3B_Wilson.2C_Richard.3B_Simon.2C_Jonathan2006">Tushnet, Mark V.; Martin, Francisco Forrest; Stephen J. Schnably; Wilson, Richard; Simon, Jonathan (2006). <i>International Human Rights and Humanitarian Law: Treaties, Cases, and Analysis</i>. Cambridge, UK: Cambridge University Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0521858860" class="internal">ISBN 0-521-85886-0</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=International+Human+Rights+and+Humanitarian+Law%3A+Treaties%2C+Cases%2C+and+Analysis&amp;rft.aulast=Tushnet%2C+Mark+V.%3B+Martin%2C+Francisco+Forrest%3B+Stephen+J.+Schnably%3B+Wilson%2C+Richard%3B+Simon%2C+Jonathan&amp;rft.au=Tushnet%2C+Mark+V.%3B+Martin%2C+Francisco+Forrest%3B+Stephen+J.+Schnably%3B+Wilson%2C+Richard%3B+Simon%2C+Jonathan&amp;rft.date=2006&amp;rft.place=Cambridge%2C+UK&amp;rft.pub=Cambridge+University+Press&amp;rft.isbn=0-521-85886-0&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Waterboarding"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
