<li><a href="http://jurist.law.pitt.edu/paperchase/2008/02/europe-rights-court-upholds-absolute.php" class="external text" title="http://jurist.law.pitt.edu/paperchase/2008/02/europe-rights-court-upholds-absolute.php" rel="nofollow">Europe rights court upholds absolute torture ban in Tunisia deportation case</a> by Brett Murphy, JURIST, February 28, 2008</li>
